data.description: Discover this pristine twin home! A serene front courtyard with a tiled entry invites you in. Ample storage throughout -- both bedrooms boast spacious walk-in closets -- complemented by additional garage storage. Elevated toilets and granite-topped high vanities add a touch of luxury. Enjoy the secluded charm of the screened-in back patio. The kitchen features a raised ceiling, recessed lighting, and a convenient no-touch faucet. You'll love the spacious garage with a 23' tandem extension for 2 cars and a golf cart. HOA pays water/sewer/trash and leased solar at $119/mo helps keep the utilities super affordable. Low-maintenance landscaping enhances the tranquility of this peaceful community.
